When on a trip to Hyderabad , my cousin suggested that this place has the best shawarma and being a shawarma lover , I badly wanted to try it !! 
So ordered it in @swiggy ..
The packing was so damn good.. wrapped In aluminium foil and packed inside a box.. it was a delight to open it ..
The shawarma was so juicy and fresh with lump sum amount of chicken .. the kubus was so fresh and soft .. 
no doubt that it’s one of the top three shawarma I’ve ever had ..

I have ordered food from here several times and was never disappointed... Not just me but colleagues at my work place also love the food here... The owner is courteous and customizes the food according to our instructions.. Extremely pocket friendly and the biryani here is flavourful.. Cant compare it to hyd biryani though... But still provides great taste... As it is pocket friendly i almost order food during month ends... A definite place to try food from... The biryani feels like home made and they make it spicy if instructed... All in all i love the food here...

The best place to get a biriyani from. 
The actual North Indian biriyani taste.
Also you should try fry biriyani it is awesome.
Not a place to dine in but definitely a place to order from.
